{"tid":1918863,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"江敏強不滿屯門區議會言論 拉隊離場","createTime":"2020-03-10T11:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T11:38:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6cedbd8e7a87af3cfee0fd8ad0ed8fc6c5248f3a","tid":1918863,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"【屯門區議會 警方拉隊離場】<br />\n<br />\n屯門區議會今日召開會議，警方屯門區指揮官江敏強出席匯報區內治安情況。席間兆翠區議員甄霈霖發言時提及，去年 10 月 1 日 18 歲中五生曾志健中槍入院，當時有一隊防暴警察在無戴口罩情況下進入醫院，批評警員「污糟邋遢」。<br />\n<br />\n江敏強不滿甄霈霖言論，要求屯門區議會主席陳樹英裁定甄言論冒犯。惟陳樹英指，每個人對該番言論的理解不同，認為言論不算冒犯，並指議會有大量議程尚待處理，拒絕作裁決。江敏強其後表示，他們不能再繼續參與會議，與其他警方人員拉隊離場。<br />\n<br />\n片段：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3aTJWJd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aTJWJd&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=68746c2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3aTJWJd</a>"},{"pid":"3d9d307a05746aea752ef6d9407e618d457fd000","tid":1918863,"uid":98386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:18:29.000Z","msg":"唔啱聽就走人 邊到搵呢啲工"},{"pid":"705a4e1b5a859688ba2228ba678d19304fa2cd97","tid":1918863,"uid":192824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:18:29.000Z","msg":"走啦，死撚哂佢，唔好再返黎TIM 呀，男人婆"},{"pid":"bee697d934a2403d516fd8b312cdb60c47069f21","tid":1918863,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"死遠D啦"},{"pid":"513974ac924617eec9ca7da86ce0d86ce167e781","tid":1918863,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"Bye bye好行唔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989351eb793d31799e944aae9e93044fffb51576","tid":1918863,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"死警甴"},{"pid":"930aa4ce948d95e12151